lead_paragraph: Those arrested, the Interior Ministry said, recently returned to Spain after going to Ukraine last year to join pro-Russian troops around Luhansk and Donetsk.

headline.main: Spain Arrests 8 on Suspicion of Fighting for Rebels in Ukraine
